                    <WebAddress>https://www.adb.org/about/history</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>History</Header>
                <Paragraph>Conceived in the early 1960s as a financial institution that would be Asian in character and foster economic growth and cooperation in one of the poorest regions in the world, the ADB opened in the Philippine capital of Manila in 1966. To learn about the Bank's initial achievements and those of more recent decades, visit the "ADB History" web page.</Paragraph>
